# ── AIFUT .dockerignore — strip build context fat ──
# Goal: keep Docker build context minimal & images lean.

# Dependencies (re-installed inside the image)
**/node_modules
**/.pnp
**/.pnp.js

# Build outputs (rebuilt inside the image)
**/dist
**/build
**/.next
**/out
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output

# Local env & secrets (NEVER ship into images)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/*.pem
**/*.key

# Logs & runtime junk
**/*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
**/.cache

# Version control & CI
.git
.gitignore
.github
**/.gitkeep

# Editor / OS noise
.vscode
.idea
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
*.swp

# Docs & local-only material
**/*.md
!**/README.md
docs
memory
infra/regions/**/.env.region

# Tests & tooling configs not needed at runtime
**/*.test.ts
**/*.spec.ts
**/__tests__
**/jest.config.*
**/.eslintcache
